title: The Witcher ebooks
description:
My first upload. All 5 Witcher ebooks in EPUB format (there are 7 Witcher books in total but the other 2 don't have official English translations, yet). I'm currently reading the books myself so I'll correct any issues I encounter. Please provide feedback if you find any errors instead of downvoting the torrent, thank you.

IMPORTANT NOTE:

To avoid spoilers, read the books in the order they're numbered (from 1 to 5)
